title: Monash Uni recruitment link

embed.description: Create a new survey on your own or with others at the same time. Choose from a variety of survey types and analyze results in Google Forms. Free from Google.

body:
For anyone in joining a team at monash uni, Please fill out the form and I will get back to you ASAP

If you have any questions just ask here and I will respond

Also if you looking for a casual place to meet other LoL players Clayton has The Society of Video Games appreciation
https://www.facebook.com/groups/22876755083/

replies.body: Hi I am moving to Monash at June 20th I am from singapore. I will be moving there soon, I was wondering if anyone is up for duoing sometime later this month. I am league of legends player from SEA and TW servers. I am looking to rank up on an account at oce reigon, I might be a bit rusty but I should get back up to speed real fast if I have enough time.
